title: Love Story (Taylor's Version)
description:
Taylor Swift was a young girl that wrote this song in a matter of minutes... but there is a lot to discuss here! Who inspired it? And why did the Shakespeare stans get upset?
Amy, Ana, Lacey and Nick dive deep into this classic song and find the real meaning behind it, and what "Romeo" has said since the song's release.
What are your thoughts on this song? What did we miss? Hit us up and tell us everything!
